This application is a supplications application provided by the Sabily community.

the file format is like this
@key=value
or
@key
multiline value
the initial space is stripped

an empty line marks a paragrpha in text

a full file would look like this

@lang=ar
@ref=B
@id=789
@text
اللهم إني أعوذ بك من عذاب القبر وأعوذ بك من فتنة المسيح الدجال وأعوذ
بك من فتنة المحيا وفتنة الممات اللهم إني أعوذ بك من المأثم والمغرم
@links
http://hadith.al-islam.com/Display/Display.asp?Doc=1&Rec=159	more from al-islam.com
http://www.islamweb.net/newlibrary/display_book.php?flag=1&bk_no=54&ID=7044	more from islamweb.net
http://www.quranexplorer.com/Hadith/English/Hadith/bukhari/002.021.221.html	full hadith in English
@media=B789.ogg




All Athkar are currently from:
  * صحيح بخاري
  * صحيح مسلم
  * سنن الترمذي

I don't want to change that for now, no athkar from different sources are allowed


